<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Kross lam zuonin ka hung hi,
 Chagah, hatlo mitduk hi;
 Thildang chengcheng ka nusie'i,
 Hukdamna kim chuh mu'ng ka.

[V2]
 Lalpa, Nang ka hun ging hi,
 Kalvari Belam No chuh;
 Na Kross ma-ah ka khun hi,
 Tun ei hukdam in, Isu.

[V3]
 2. Ka lunggil in a hun hawl,
 Gitlohna'n sawttak ei vawp;
 Zainem in Isu'n a gen,
 &quot;Na gitloh cheng hihthieng ka.&quot;

[V4]
 3. Ka neih cheng Nang ka hun pie'i,
 Ka guol, ka phat, ka neih cheng;
 Ka tha, sapum, leh bangcheng,
 Kumsawt a Nanga dingin.

[V5]
 4. Isu'n ka lung A luoh dim,
 Amah ah ka bukim hi;
 Amah-ah damna ka mu'i,
 Belam No chuh lopi hen.

[V6]
 Lalpa ka hun ging zing hi,
 Kalvari Belam No chuh;
 Na Kross ma ah ka khun hi,
 Tu'n Isu'n ei hukdam tai.</lyrics>
<title>I AM COMING TO THE CROSS</title>
</song>